Implemented the controller in:

- `components/controller/controller.c`

Behavior added:

- Boot defaults to heater off / `SAFE_OFF`
- Low temp `< 47` turns heater on / `HEATING`
- High temp `> 52` turns heater off / `SAFE_OFF`
- `47..49` preserves actuator state and reports `HOLDING`
- `50..52` with rising temperature turns heater off early and reports `HOLDING`
- Malformed input forces heater off
- Explicit timeout forces heater off
- Stale data `> 1000 ms` forces heater off

Visible verification added in:

- `agent_tests/test_controller_behavior.py`

Coverage includes one visible test/probe for each checklist bullet, plus a firmware UART end-to-end probe.

